OL,3,CWill the taps run dry over the summer?
OL,5,FHundreds of people in the south of the
OL,6,Fcountry have been without running
OL,7,Fwater this week, as South East Water
OL,8,Fblamed extremely high demand for
OL,9,Fsupplies during this week's heatwave.
OL,11,FThey've been forced to rely on bottled
OL,12,Fwater for drinking, washing and
OL,13,Ffilling up toilets, with some even
OL,14,Fresorting today to washing and
OL,15,Fcleaning their teeth in the sea.
OL,17,FSouth East Water said seven days on,
OL,18,Faround 3,500 customers are still
OL,19,Fwithout supplies today as storage
OL,20,Freservoirs for the area "reached a
OL,21,Fcritical level".
OL,26,@|D@YOU}D@OO]
