OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780323077
OL,3,CWill the taps run dry over the summer?
OL,5,FSouth Staffs Water said: "Last year we
OL,6,Fsaw a drought in our South Staffs
OL,7,FWater region, but through our response
OL,8,Fto the drought and our customers using
OL,9,Fwater wisely, we did not need to
OL,10,Fimplement a hosepipe ban.
OL,12,F"This year our reservoir level is 13%
OL,13,Fhigher than at this time last year.
OL,15,F"We continuously monitor water
OL,16,Fresources across our network to ensure
OL,17,Fwe can meet customer demand, whilst
OL,18,Fprotecting the environment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780323077
OL,3,CWill the taps run dry over the summer?
OL,5,F"As always, we encourage customers to
OL,6,Fuse water wisely, particularly during
OL,7,Fwarmer and drier periods, as small
OL,8,Fchanges in everyday habits can make a
OL,9,Fsignificant difference in helping to
OL,10,Fprotect this vital resource.
OL,12,F"We remain committed to transparency
OL,13,Fand will keep customers and
OL,14,Fstakeholders informed should
OL,15,Fcircumstances change."
OL,17,FMeanwhile, South East Water say they
OL,18,Fexpect supplies to continue to be
OL,19,Fintermittent for some customers until
OL,20,Ftemperatures decrease and demand
OL,21,Freduces.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
